  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Transforming livelihoods and early education in Upper East Region, Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will provide 210 children between the ages of one and six with a safe space to learn, play and eat a nutritious meal every day. 210 children will benefit every year, meaning that this project will impact thousands of children long in to the future. In order to address other barriers to children&amp;rsquo;s education, we will also provide access to clean water at the centres and support community members to increase their incomes.</narrative>
  </description>
